          "reviewBody": "The school follows unethical admission practices by making false commitments to parents in order to secure admissions. The admission counsellor, Ms. Pratima, repeatedly pressures parents through persistent follow-ups and gives assurances that are not honoured later. Once parents realise that the promised commitments are not being fulfilled and decide to withdraw the admission, the school refuses to refund the fees. This appears to be a recurring pattern. Parents are advised to be cautious and consider taking appropriate legal action to address this malpractice.",
