          "reviewBody": "The journey of my daughter at vishwajyot is really memorable.\nAs ICSE curriculum is really vast and the concepts are difficult to teach of few subjects\nBut the teachers  with there innovative methods and versatile teaching techniques  have made learning easy and enjoyable\nAppreciate the efforts of the teachers and management for grooming my child so well",
