            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My son has been studying for the past 5 years in this school. The best thing about this school is it doesn't put much pressure on students to perform. Not much homework. Most concepts taught in a practical way and still students seem to be performing very well. They have overall development where kids are encouraged to participate in activities like sports & various cultural events. Even during Covid they found creative ways to engage students and conducted all activities as per the academic calender. The set up and feel of the school is also very pleasing and have experienced teaching staff. They help students by giving personal attention and care. I'm glad my son is a part of this school",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
